  <name>Calculus</name>
  <summary>Compute derivatives and integrals</summary>
	<description>
	  <p>A practical tool to foresee the result of calculus exercises.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Compute derivatives</li>
      <li>Compute integrals</li>
      <li>Plot the original expression and result within a given range</li>
    </ul>
	  <p>
	    If you are interested, open an issue in github to update a translation or make a pull request.
      All available translations:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>English</li>
      <li>Portuguese</li>
      <li>Italian (outdated)</li>
      <li>Spanish (outdated)</li>
      <li>Slovakian (outdated)</li>
    </ul>
	</description>
